	   <tr><td colspan=2>IN regards to the eternal "what weapon" specialization for the shaman question, some observations after 35 lvls:<br>-you will only be able to keep up one weapons skill after about lvl 20 - you group a lot as a healer and don't get to mellee.<br>- go 2HB if you want to solo/mellee - most damage<br>- go piercing if you want to be loved in group with lots of mana available and a decent damage <br><br>ideal equipment for piercing/mana<br>primary - slime coated harpoon 10/25 <br>secondary - charred guardian shield <br>range - howling harpoon<br>+ 25 wis, + 10 mana<br>cost about 2000 pp<br><br>ideal for mellee<br>drakeel hammer 27/45<br>cost about 200&nbsp;&nbsp;pp<br>+either wis or AC item for range<br>full totemic armor, cost min 1500 pp if quested, 5000 pp if bought <br><br>all within easy range by 35 untwinked,<br>I personally went the piercing route<br><br>Shamu Whitewale<br>35 bar shm Xev<br>&nbsp;<br>Shamu Whitewale<br>Prophet, Xev<br></td></tr>
